xmlSingleDriverDefinition.name: Ensoniq ESQ-1 Single
xmlSingleDriverDefinition.infoText: Whenever JSynthLib sends a Patch to the ESQ, the synthesizer will go to a screen where you must hit 'exit' on the front panel before you can send another patch. This is kind of annoying, so if anyone knows a way around this let me know. The other ESQ librarians I checked out had the same problem, so it may be impossible
